Package main.model

Class RequestInfo

java.lang.Object
main.model.RequestInfo
public class RequestInfo extends Object
RequestInfo Class Contains the request information from Ngo. It contains Ngo name, Manpower, Requested aids, Aids quantity, Remaining requested item quantity and Donor who donated the aids.
